# Phase 2 H.0: ALL local credential files live under functions/secrets/ —
# directory-scoped ignore so any key name (e.g. tofes-mecher-sa.json) is safe,
# not just `service-account*`-prefixed names. (outcomes-grader H.0 finding.)
functions/secrets/

